            <p>In Araneta Center Cubao, there is daily roll-on roll-off (Roro) trip which leaves Manila at 1:00 PM. The Mega Bus and Elavil Bus have daily trips from Manila to Masbate via Pilar port.</p>
            <p>From Cebu, a Roro bus leaves at 7:30 PM in Bogo every Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays. Via Trans Asia, Cebu- Masbate route is every Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays. Masbate can also be reached through the sea onboard luxury shipping lines like the Shuttle Roro (Batangas-Mas- bate every Tuesdays, 3:00 PM; Cebu-Masbate, every Sun- days, 5:00 AM) and MV Mary the Queen (Masbate-Manila- Masbate every Tuesday, 10:00 AM)</p>
